@lacoste and @alpinecars have teamed up for one of the most playful concepts at Paris Fashion Week: the one-off Alpine A290 Rallye dressed in the French label's unmistakable crocodile codes. From the iconic red of the croc's tongue to Alpine-inspired shades of icy blue and white, the rally car blends motorsport performance with Lacoste's signature identity.⁠
⁠
Inside, the details get even better. Lacoste's classic petit piqué fabric covers the seats and door panels, while a crocodile lurks in the rear of the cabin as if chasing the clock. Alpine even crowns the driver the "Crocopilot," turning every stage into a hunt for the perfect racing line.

@prada is the latest luxury label to join forces with @gentlemonster. First teased during Paris Fashion Week, the collaboration delivers three eyewear designs that blend the Korean label's futuristic edge with Prada's refined aesthetic. Sharp lens shapes, architectural frames, titanium temples, and a sideways Prada logo give the collection a subtle twist, while a campaign starring Prada ambassador Kentaro Sakaguchi brings the release to life through a story inspired by the elements.⁠
⁠
The Prada x Gentle Monster collection launches in select Asian markets, including Japan, South Korea, and Mainland China, with Japan getting an in-store release on July 6 followed by an online launch on July 7. The partnership also continues Gentle Monster's growing streak of high-profile collaborations, following Maison Margiela and ahead of its much-anticipated Google project.

@Barbie dà il benvenuto alla superstar mondiale @MileyCyrus nella serie Barbie Signature™, con il lancio di una nuova bambola da collezione ispirata all’icona del pop. La bambola celebra l’impronta culturale che Miley ha lasciato come musicista, attrice e sostenitrice dell’espressione di sé, rendendo omaggio ai suoi successi da record. Completo in similpelle firmato Alaïa, giacca con cappuccio, pumps a punta, occhiali da sole e microfono. «Vedere la mia Barbie per la prima volta è un sogno che si avvera», ha detto Miley. Nell’anno del ventennale di “Hannah Montana” e della sua stella sulla Hollywood Walk of Fame, l’icona diventa da collezione.
Photo: Courtesy of Mattel
